| `app/api/admin/ghl-subaccounts/link/route.js` | **Bug Fix (GHL Link)**: Fixed `23505 duplicate key` crash on `location_id` unique constraint. When re-linking a location already held by another user, the route now: (1) deactivates any conflicting row from other users, (2) deletes the old physical row for that location_id, and (3) re-inserts with the new owner. Previously would return 500 on conflict. Also hotfixed Debra Shelton's row directly via SQL (`is_active = false → true` for location `nGGnFrvFOelEOy2kjFlo`). |
| `app/api/admin/funnels/route.js` | **Feature (Undeploy)**: Added `undeploy` action to the admin funnels PUT handler. Sets `deployed_at = NULL` — clears the funnel's deployed state without touching approvals, so the user can trigger a full new deployment from the Vault. |
